an adequate amount of sleep or not. An easy example: your brain resembles a car and having some rest is a petrol. When the petrol runs out, the car stops and does not move forward, so does your brain. As simple as it is. You are still here and thinking that relaxing is irrelevant? See the difference after devoting at least 7 hours per day at sleeping. It is not a threat but a high recommendation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Eat<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Eating, as is known, plays a great role in one&#8217;s well-being and you can, unfortunately, do nothing to change this statement. Do not skip breakfast, decrease the number of carbs but do not deprive yourself of an opportunity to eat with great relish.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"http:\/\/nordthemes.com\/iceberg\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2015\/12\/photo-1458819757519-7581bade511d-1024x682.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-108\" srcset=\"https:\/\/nordthemes.com\/iceberg\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2015\/12\/photo-1458819757519-7581bade511d-1024x682.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/nordthemes.com\/iceberg\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2015\/12\/photo-1458819757519-7581bade511d-300x200.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/nordthemes.com\/iceberg\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2015\/12\/photo-1458819757519-7581bade511d-768x511.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/nordthemes.com\/iceberg\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2015\/12\/photo-1458819757519-7581bade511d-1200x799.jpeg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Consuming alcohol may lead you to a resentment rather than to a satisfaction so in both cases you need to know when enough is enough and that is it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Fresh air and exercises<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It should come as no surprise that besides sleeping and energy our brain and body requires to change the subject of activity to relax from the routine. Lack of motion can affect your mood and cause tiredness. Who needs this? Indeed, nobody. The easiest way to avoid that situation is to simply take a walk or do some exercises. Do not demand a lot from yourself: 20-30 minutes of walking will completely switch your way of thinking and bring some strength to attain your aims.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http:\/\/nordthemes.com\/iceberg\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2015\/12\/SimoneAnne-1862-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-41\" srcset=\"https:\/\/nordthemes.com\/iceberg\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2015\/12\/SimoneAnne-1862-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/nordthemes.com\/iceberg\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2015\/12\/SimoneAnne-1862-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/nordthemes.com\/iceberg\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2015\/12\/SimoneAnne-1862-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/nordthemes.com\/iceberg\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2015\/12\/SimoneAnne-1862-1200x800.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Have you ever realized that prep can be bearable and even interesting? I bet you have not. Having friend, some good music and a plan &#8211; three items you should follow. Divide the materials that are to learn and then paraphrase them to each other to facilitate the studying and make it easier to remember. The point is that it can be hard to not digress on another topic but do not give up, okay?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Goals are great but the feeling of achievement is better, isn&#8217;t it? Make your journey full of that kind of moments and good luck!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Just remind yourself how many times you have already checked an alarm clock in order to check it again. Typical. Maybe after that go to bed dreaming about a better life without complications such as exams and throbbing headache. And, of course, the